{"tid":363033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事小故事]一個人既極致","createTime":"2017-08-17T10:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T10:53:59.000Z","uid":114563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3db09a78abb77b226009bbdf202e4952445010","tid":363033,"uid":114563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"話說.....<br />\n今日準備去一個泰國既主題樂園<br />\n去到既時候一個人都無<br />\n成個樂園差唔多得我地呢團人<br />\n咁之後去玩水啦<br />\n玩完水就出黎玩機動遊戲啦<br />\n行行下見到一個人排緊隊<br />\n係一個人！！！<br />\n咁之後要等職員開比佢玩<br />\n之後我好唔掙氣咁<br />\n睇住佢暏係佢一個人玩<br />\n一個差唔多有三十座位既過山車<br />\n佢坐在係中間 無表情咁就玩完過山車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.s樂園包括水上樂園同埋機動遊戲個部份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cd789d40edb6f77acb2fb5a0efcf3cccec0939","tid":363033,"uid":114563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"最後一個人就走左<br />\n再見唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}